OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy and
OL,6,Fdamp during Thursday evening with
OL,7,Fspells of rain and drizzle. Some drier
OL,8,Fand clearer intervals developing
OL,9,Fovernight, though drizzle still
OL,10,Fpossible over the hills and a breeze
OL,11,Fpicking up into the early hours of
OL,12,FFriday. A mild night.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FCloudy start. A band of rain
OL,15,Fthen moves eastwards, initially patchy
OL,16,Fbut potentially turning heavier in the
OL,17,Fafternoon. Late sunny spells emerging
OL,18,Ffor the evening as the breeze
OL,19,Fgradually eases.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
