OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Flargely fine and dry weekend as high
OL,7,Fpressure builds. Feeling pleasant in
OL,8,Fany sunshine and lighter winds.
OL,9,FPerhaps more cloud around on Monday
OL,10,Fbut staying dry with near-average
OL,11,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
